title: Horizontal
typeOfFood: Vegan, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out
description: Vegan restaurant in Etazhi loft project ground floor, established by Chiapas restobar in 2014. Old school vegan kitchen crew, offering burgers and wraps (falafel, tofu, seitan), rolls, salads, plus freshly squeezed juices, and shakes. Delivers Mon-Fri 1-8pm.
